" Use s to replace the first match of a search
" while search highlighting is enabled
function! KillNextHighlighted()
  if &hlsearch == 1
    call feedkeys("cgn")
  endif
endfunction
nmap s :call KillNextHighlighted()<CR>

" Make it possible to go to a numbered line via CR
nnoremap <CR> G

